data.name: label3.Text
data.value:
Ever used Toad's Tool 64/Quad64? These controls should be familiar, except for the ROT box.
The ROT box changes cam rotation. Works like C-Up mode, drag it the same way as the POS box.
Important: like with the Dolphin camera hack, Mario's "forward" direction isn't aligned with the camera, but we'll try to make it so. Be careful when moving in Super Hard Freeze!
Hover over the buttons to get more information.

data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Protip: You can drag the bottom or top of the window and shrink the controls window to just look at the Timeline so you have more vertical space.
Looking for more? You can click "File" to access load/save.
